text: Undiscovered country may refer to: *Undiscovered Country, the 1979 play by Tom Stoppard * The Undiscovered Country, the 1998 album (and song) by the Swedish band Destiny * "The undiscover'd country...", from the "To be, or not to be" soliloquy in Hamlet * Star Trek VI: The Undiscovered Country, a 1991 film
title: Undiscovered country
